    q: 'Is Salerno the better interchange?',
    a: 'Use Salerno for Amalfi, Atrani, Ravello, Maiori, and Minori. For Positano, compare live ferry departures from Naples Beverello and Salerno, then choose the port that has the best realistic departure after your flight.',
